version_description: This version is similar to version 2. The only differences are that the verse is now G6 - G, to combine the lead guitar with the rhythm guitar for acoustic playing. Second thing is, they play a D7 in the intro.
Correct chords in key, chords guide, right alignment between chords and lyrics.

It gives a clear show of how the tab should look for beginners/intermediates. It clearly shows what chords to use at exactly the right time of the lyrics. And the whole thing is very easy to understand.
